WEBVTT

1
00:01.200 --> 00:04.240
I open like a room remembering itself.

2
00:09.800 --> 00:13.320
Inside the pulse, another pulse keeps watch.

3
00:17.000 --> 00:21.480
At the brightest edge, the image folds inward and sings.

4
00:27.600 --> 00:31.280
Then everything thins to a small true glimmer.

